metadata.name: GainPepeChecked
metadata.description:
This is a first project to remind everyone in the space, what's most important. Yes, you read right its "health".  
Goal of this collection is to form a community where we help each other in improving our lifestyle, motivate each other, lift each other.  
Mint amount will be distributed among holders as price to participate in activities, holders will need to workout for 22 days in 30 day period.  
Workout can be anything- yoga, gym, running, athlete workout etc. Will need to submit a proof of every workout. Prices will be decided based on total minted funds. 
More surprises cooking.  
Everyone who completes the task within timeframe and submits proof of regular workout  will win.  
Less Go!!
